0 @S2@ SOUR
1 TITL Norwegian in 5 Minutes a Month
1 ABBR Norwegian in 5 Minutes a Month
1 AUTH Sons of Norway
1 PUBL Sons of Norway
1 REPO @REPO2@
1 TEXT Our monthly language lesson has been out for a while now, and many of you have let us know that it is working well. Thank you for taking the time to communicate with us.
2 CONT
2 CONT Visitors to "Norwegian in 5 Minutes a Month" have asked for information on the Norwegian alphabet and genealogical terms, so we have added pages on both topics. We look forward to your feedback. In the meantime, good luck!
2 CONT
2 CONT http://www.sofn.com/norwegian_culture/languagelessons_index.jsp
