1 REPO @REPO3@
1 TEXT The following marriage index is being created by using the microfilms that contain copies of the actual marriage licenses and marriage certificates. The index contains the book and page where the certificate can be found, name of groom or bride
2 CONC , name of bride or groom, marriage license date and place and date of marriage and place.
2 CONT
